HEADWORD: Supertuberation
<hw>Su`per*tu`ber*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>super-</ets> + <ets>tuber</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The
